question: Lily is required to submit a 153-page thesis. She already finished writing 1/3 of the thesis. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Lily has already written 1/3 of the thesis which is 153 pages*1/3 = <<153*1/3=51>>51 pages.
So, she still needs to write 153 pages - 51 pages = <<153-51=102>>102 pages.
#### 102
